## DESIGN CONSTRAINTS

- All screens: gnBgDeepest background, gnBgSurface cards, gnBorderCard 1dp stroke, no elevation
- Fonts: GameNativeFontFamily (Outfit) via PluviaTypography everywhere
- No new colors — only existing gn_* tokens
- Section headers: 11sp gnTextTertiary uppercase letterSpacing=0.10
- Sliders: use Material3 Slider with gnAccentPrimary thumb and track
- Toggles: use Material3 Switch with gnAccentPrimary checked color
- Preset chips: same FilterChip style as LibraryListPane sort chips
- Config cards: group related settings inside a single Card (gnBgSurface)
  with Dividers between rows — don't make every setting its own card
- All hardware reads on Dispatchers.IO, never on main thread
- Cache HardwareProfile in DataStore — only re-detect on first run or app update
- KnownGameFixes is a hardcoded in-app database that ships with the app
  AND can be updated via a remote JSON endpoint for new game fixes
  without requiring an app update
